SB 131 Reengrossed 2026 Regular Session Pressly
Present law (R.S. 37:21(B)) provides that the provisions of present law (R.S. 37:21) do not
apply to certain professional or occupational licensing boards.
Proposed law provides that the provisions of present law (R.S. 37:21(A)) do not apply to
certain professional or occupational licensing boards.
